name: Web App UI Kit
description: Trim is a task management web app UI kit that lets you easily create and monetize all your work. With unlimited projects and unlimited collaborators, This product lets you control your team. With Trim, you can easily organize your team work, manage to-do's and tasks, assign projects to your clients and staff, monitor workflow progress. Trim has proven to be an efficient & powerful task management web app for business startups. Here you can easily get your team's daily, monthly, weekly work reports. You Can Easily Customize This Design file. Your users will love your site because it gives them a unique user experience (UX), clean, modern & beautiful design. Well, layered and organized, responsive resize, global color and text styles, and with free fonts family from Google Fonts (Inter).
